episode of.title: Cash in the Celebrity Attic (TV Series 2008– )

13.plot: Singer-songwriter Lynsey de Paul welcomes presenter Lorne Spicer and the Cash in the Celebrity Attic team into her home in London,U.K. Lynsey hopes to raise 500 pounds for the Wildlife Rescue and Ambulance Service. She manages to auction some interesting items, including one bought for her by James Coburn and even becomes the auctioneer.

imdb.plot outline: Well-known British celebrities rummage for collectables and antiques in their homes to take to auction, the intention being to raise money for donation to their favourite charities. In series one, the highest amounts were raised by entertainer Brian Conley and TV presenter Nick Hancock.
